content: Great just wish it could show mortgage insurance in the piti
replyContent: Thank you Carol! After you've entered your inputs, a dollar sign icon appears in the display. Tap the dollar sign to see the details of the PITI payment. PITI payment includes the monthly tax, insurance and mortgage insurance amounts if entered. Please reach us at techsupport@calculated.com for more help.

content: Mortgage related calculator. I love the calculator, wish it had voice recognition capability.
If I went out and bought the actual calculator it would have cost me 45-55 bucks and I wouldn't have the ability to email items!!!!

This app gave me iPhone envy. Now it is finally ported to android, and it was worth the wait.   This calculator is the best around for Realtors and is normally $70 in the stores.   Download it at the bargain prices and always have it with you.
